配置 HTTPS
Nginx：

server {
    listen 443 ssl;
    server_name example.com;

    ssl_certificate /etc/ssl/cert.pem;
    ssl_certificate_key /etc/ssl/key.pem;

    location / {
        proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:8080;
    }
}
重载：
nginx -t
systemctl reload nginx
访问：
https://example.com
